OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with some late
OL,7,Fbrightness for Shetland, but outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain soon arriving for Orkney. Rain
OL,9,Fturns heavy for a time as it spreads
OL,10,Fto Shetland overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA cloudy and wet start for
OL,13,FShetland, but drier and brighter for
OL,14,FOrkney. Sunny spells developing as
OL,15,Frain clears Shetland, but a few
OL,16,Fafternoon showers developing for
OL,17,FOrkney.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
